### Problem12

Look at the following java code:

```java
public class AddOne
{
    public static void main(String[]args)
    {
        System.out.println(args[0]+1);
    }
}
```

What is the output if we do:
javac AddOne.java
java AddOne 3 1

**Choices:**

a. 4

b. 2

c. AddOne1

d. 31

e. compile-time error
